<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/934417-are-insects-animals">Are insects animals?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_934417'><a id="like_count_community_question_934417" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/934417?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">6 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F30231743-are-we-smart-enough-to-know-how-smart-animals-are">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/934417-are-insects-animals">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/934417-are-insects-animals">See all 8 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
