          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781783783045" href="/book/show/31822229-are-we-smart-enough-to-know-how-smart-animals-are">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7706640-jami?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7706640-jami?shelf=2018-reads">2018-reads</a>
          </div>
